BlueTextRequest - Class in bigsky
Request object for communication between PC and android
BlueTextRequest(BlueTextRequest.REQUEST, Contact) - Constructor for class bigsky.BlueTextRequest
Constructor for a request.
BlueTextRequest.REQUEST - Enum in bigsky
Requests used to ask for data from the phone: PING: Tests the connection between phone and computer CONTACT_CHAT_HISTORY: Asks for ArrayList of TextMessages representing chat history with that user or users.
BlueTextResponse - Class in bigsky
Response object for communication between PC and Android
BlueTextResponse(BlueTextRequest, Object...) - Constructor for class bigsky.BlueTextResponse
A Response must be created with the original BlueTextRequest and additional arguments depending on what the original request is: REQUESTObjects... CONTACT_CHAT_HISTORY 0: ArrayList{TextMessage} BATTERY_PERCENTAGE 0: Integer CONTACT_PICTURE 0: Boolean 1: obj[0] ? Byte[] : String
